28
00:00:48,880 --> 00:00:50,279
(He does have a point.)

29
00:00:50,560 --> 00:00:51,520
(It'll be my loss if I don't take it.)

30
00:00:52,000 --> 00:00:52,880
Don't worry.

31
00:00:52,919 --> 00:00:54,639
Mina won't disappoint you.

32
