42
00:01:23,400 --> 00:01:24,519
They thought I was a scammer.

43
00:01:24,720 --> 00:01:26,440
You? A scammer?

44
00:01:27,040 --> 00:01:28,760
Maybe it was because of
my qualifications.

45
00:01:28,919 --> 00:01:30,720
I learned programming by myself

46
00:01:30,720 --> 00:01:32,040
when I was in America.

47
00:01:32,239 --> 00:01:33,400
It was natural for them

48
00:01:33,400 --> 00:01:34,639
to discriminate against me
and not believe in me

49
00:01:34,639 --> 00:01:35,480
as I didn't graduate from a famous university.

50
00:01:36,360 --> 00:01:38,720
