51
00:01:40,120 --> 00:01:41,080
I persisted because of my dream.

52
00:01:42,440 --> 00:01:43,160
It's because...

53
00:01:46,319 --> 00:01:47,639
I wanted you to notice me.

54
00:01:51,279 --> 00:01:52,919
That's a great joke.

55
00:02:14,759 --> 00:02:16,000
What are you doing here?

56
00:02:16,800 --> 00:02:17,520
I'm working out.

57
00:02:18,479 --> 00:02:20,600
You came all the way north
from the south just to work out?

58
00:02:20,679 --> 00:02:22,240
I love to run around the city.

59
00:02:23,440 --> 00:02:25,320
Weiyi, I can tell you don't jog often.

60
00:02:25,559 --> 00:02:27,039
