61
00:02:27,320 --> 00:02:28,399
Is there something on your mind?

62
00:02:34,720 --> 00:02:35,600
Let's relax.

63
00:02:47,880 --> 00:02:49,080
Weiyi, since when

64
00:02:49,080 --> 00:02:50,240
did you start to drink?

65
00:02:52,360 --> 00:02:53,800
After I started to work.

66
00:02:54,279 --> 00:02:56,240
I had no choice but to entertain
my clients due to my career.

67
00:02:56,479 --> 00:02:57,800
I learned how to drink eventually.

68
00:02:58,800 --> 00:03:00,360
Weiyi, I remembered

69
00:03:00,800 --> 00:03:02,320
that you said drinking
is bad for our health.

70
00:03:04,919 --> 00:03:06,880
Between surviving
and having a healthy body,

71
00:03:07,479 --> 00:03:10,199
I have no choice but to pick the former.

72
00:03:23,559 --> 00:03:25,119
Weiyi, did you dump me

73
00:03:25,559 --> 00:03:26,880
only to get revenge back then?

74
00:03:33,720 --> 00:03:35,320
The god of destiny makes fools
of the people indeed.

75
00:03:36,759 --> 00:03:38,119
Have you ever regretted your decision?

76
00:03:40,639 --> 00:03:41,720
That's a secret.

77
00:03:41,720 --> 00:03:43,679
♪The road to your heart is so long♪

78
00:03:43,679 --> 00:03:45,160
But I wish to know it badly.

79
00:03:48,759 --> 00:03:49,919
All men

80
00:03:50,559 --> 00:03:51,880
say they love you

81
00:03:52,240 --> 00:03:53,720
when they're in love with you.

82
00:03:54,960 --> 00:03:56,240
But in fact,

83
00:03:56,240 --> 00:03:57,479
♪The silly smile on your face♪

84
00:03:57,479 --> 00:03:59,960
they only love themselves.

85
00:04:00,024 --> 00:04:02,639
♪Is engraved on my heart♪

86
00:04:02,639 --> 00:04:04,479
I don't want to...

87
00:04:05,600 --> 00:04:08,880
I don't want to end up
in such a wretched state anymore.

88
00:04:08,880 --> 00:04:10,800
♪The wandering me
is afraid of missing you♪

89
00:04:12,114 --> 00:04:15,634
♪My heart has skipped a beat♪

90
00:04:16,018 --> 00:04:19,538
♪Whose breathing is getting weaker?♪

91
00:04:19,989 --> 00:04:21,480
♪I don't wish to argue who's at fault♪

92
00:04:21,480 --> 00:04:23,000
I missed you.

93
00:04:23,480 --> 00:04:24,760
Don't leave me.

94
00:04:24,760 --> 00:04:26,160
Stay here with me.

95
00:04:28,016 --> 00:04:31,088
♪Please forgive my stubbornness♪

96
00:04:31,536 --> 00:04:35,632
♪The promise which was almost forgotten♪

97
